          <li><a href='http://www.suntimes.com/lifestyles/lavin/index.html'>Cheryl Lavin</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://blogs.suntimes.com/cubs'>Inside the Cubs</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://www.suntimes.com/news/huntley/index.html'>Steve Huntley</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://www.suntimes.com/lifestyles/rackl/index.html'>Lori Rackl</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://blogs.suntimes.com/fire'>Inside the Fire</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://www.suntimes.com/news/jackson/index.html'>Jesse Jackson</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://www.suntimes.com/lifestyles/health/youdocs/index.html'>You Docs</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://blogs.suntimes.com/illinois'>Inside Illinois</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://www.suntimes.com/news/marin/index.html'>Carol Marin</a></li>
          <li><a href='http://blos.suntimes.com/northwestern'>Inside Northwestern</a></li>
