                <div class="comment-content">
                    <p>Roger:</p>

<p>Add a PID controller (<a href="http://auberins.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&products_id=44">Auberins</a> or <a href="http://freshmealssolutions.com/index.php?page=shop.product_details&category_id=15&flypage=shop.flypage&product_id=18&option=com_virtuemart&Itemid=26">Fresh Meals Solutions</a>) and a Foodsaver, and you can change your world forever with sous vide cookery. </p>

<p>Ok, totally not in the spirit of your post, but if you are going to limit yourself to using a rice cooker, a little bit of after-market gear can go a long way.  </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    
        
