<p>And I know Ebert already answered the guy who asked what size to get, but the sizes are listed for UNCOOKED rice.  So a 3 cup cooker will have about 9 cups of cooked rice.  Do the math on a 16 cup cooker. Too much rice for a single guy!</p>
