                        <span class="byline">
                            
        
                            <span class="vcard author">Shane</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-541028"><abbr class="published" title="2008-11-03T01:01:51-06:00">November  3, 2008  1:01 AM</abbr></a>
        
