                            <span class="vcard author">JJM</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-541432"><abbr class="published" title="2008-11-03T13:04:28-06:00">November  3, 2008  1:04 PM</abbr></a>
        
