                            <span class="vcard author">Niki</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-541593"><abbr class="published" title="2008-11-03T16:28:15-06:00">November  3, 2008  4:28 PM</abbr></a>
        
