                    <div class="asset-meta">
                        <span class="byline">
                            
        
                            <span class="vcard author"><a title="http://smrana.blogspot.com" href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/cgi-bin/mt-comments.cgi?__mode=red;id=541818">smrana</a></span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-541818"><abbr class="published" title="2008-11-03T22:24:30-06:00">November  3, 2008 10:24 PM</abbr></a>
        
