                    <p>Oh no, <i>the</i> Pot is banned here at the College of Mount St. Joseph, as are all electronic cooking devices, minus the school-supplied microwaves in the lobbies; evil, monolithic relics of a by-gone age where Hungryman dinners were considered a good decision.</p>

