                    <div class="asset-meta">
                        <span class="byline">
                            
        
                            <span class="vcard author">jim in SF</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-546340"><abbr class="published" title="2008-11-08T15:12:48-06:00">November  8, 2008  3:12 PM</abbr></a>
        
