                    <p>I tried this one over the weekend:</p>

<p>Seafood Jumbalaya</p>

<p>1lb. of peeled and deveined shrimp<br />
1 cup of white rice (use the rice cooker measuring cup)<br />
1 stick of softened butter<br />
4 oz. sliced mushrooms<br />
8 oz. crab meat (it tastes better with is real not imitation)<br />
