                <div class="comment-content">
                    <p>Rice cooker chicken spaghetti</p>

<p>Ingredients:<br />
2 cups of spaghetti noodles<br />
2 cups of pasta sauce<br />
1 cup of chopped mushrooms<br />
1 cup of chopped grilled chicken<br />
1 half a cup of shredded cheese<br />
salt</p>

<p>Instructions:<br />
* Snap spaghetti in half so it will fit into the cooker and cover with water<br />
* add just a dash of salt<br />
* Start cooking until pasta softens<br />
* Drain the pasta<br />
* Add Chicken, sauce and mushrooms<br />
* cook five minutes<br />
* add cheese<br />
* Enjoy!<br />
</p>
