                        <span class="byline">
                            
        
                            <span class="vcard author">Cheryl Knott</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-720731"><abbr class="published" title="2009-07-02T03:36:02-06:00">July  2, 2009  3:36 AM</abbr></a>
        
