                    <p>Gah! Got beaten with a jambalaya recipe! Uh, here's mine...</p>

<p>Ingredients:</p>

<p>1 cup of rice.<br />
4 oz. chicken.<br />
8 oz chicken broth.<br />
1 can of Rotel tomatoes.<br />
1 medium bell pepper, chopped.<br />
1 medium onion, chopped.<br />
1/2 stick of butter.<br />
2 tsp. cajun seasoning.<br />
1 tsp. Worcestershire sauce.<br />
1 tsp. hot sauce.<br />
1/2 tsp. salt.</p>

