                            <span class="vcard author">HopeB</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-722112"><abbr class="published" title="2009-07-04T23:33:16-06:00">July  4, 2009 11:33 PM</abbr></a>
        
