                        <span class="byline">
                            
        
                            <span class="vcard author">CHuck Seidel</span>
        
                            | <a href="http://blogs.suntimes.com/ebert/2008/11/the_pot_and_how_to_use_it.html#comment-887434"><abbr class="published" title="2010-03-11T21:29:50-06:00">March 11, 2010  9:29 PM</abbr></a>
        
